    <section id="about" class="section-white reveal visible" aria-labelledby="about-title">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="about-title">About Me</h2>

        <p class="lead">
          I'm <strong>Bharath</strong> — a dedicated Photoshop designer specialising in high-end <strong>retouching</strong>, creative <strong>image manipulations</strong>, <strong>CDP</strong> (colour and detail polishing),
          <strong>birthday designs</strong>, and attention-grabbing <strong>flyers &amp; cards</strong>. I deliver studio-quality results with a strong focus on mobile editing workflows.
        </p>

        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="about-skills">
            <h3>What I do</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Beauty &amp; fashion retouching — natural, polished results</li>
              <li>Advanced manipulations &amp; composites — creative and believable</li>
              <li>CDP — colour grading, skin tone balancing, detail enhancement</li>
              <li>Birthday invites, event cards, and promotional flyers</li>
              <li>Fast mobile editing — edits optimised for Instagram &amp; reels</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="about-process">
            <h3>How I work</h3>
            <ol>
              <li><strong>Share</strong> images &amp; brief (WhatsApp / email).</li>
              <li><strong>Proposal</strong> &amp; turnaround time (usually 24–72 hours depending on scope).</li>
              <li><strong>Draft</strong> delivered for review — two revisions included.</li>
              <li><strong>Final</strong> high-resolution files delivered (and optimized exports for web/mobile).</li>
            </ol>

            <p class="confidence">Clear pricing, quick turnaround, and friendly communication — I make the technical look effortless so your images sell.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
